      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's for lunch?",
      "zh": "午餐吃什麼？",
      "ja": "お昼は何ですか？",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fried chicken.",
      "zh": "炸雞。",
      "ja": "フライドチキン。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "French fries and salad.",
      "zh": "薯條和沙拉。",
      "ja": "フライドポテトとサラダ。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "すばらしい。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like fried chicken.",
      "zh": "我喜歡炸雞。",
      "ja": "フライドチキンが好きです。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need to wash your hands before lunch.",
      "zh": "你需要在午餐前洗手。",
      "ja": "お昼ご飯の前に手を洗う必要があります。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Kids, line up at the sink.",
